longBusinessSummary: ISW Holdings Inc., a brand management portfolio company, focuses on companies in crypto mining, renewable energy, home healthcare, wellness and restoration, and adult beverage industry sectors. It also develops supply chains and logistics management. The company was formerly known as International Spirits & Wellness Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to ISW Holdings Inc. in June 2020. ISW Holdings Inc. is based in Reno, Nevada.
